data.description: Welcome to a stunningly beautiful lake access property- Your gateway to tranquil living!     Nestled in the heart of a serene, gated community, Lake Ajay. This spectacular 4 bed, 2.5 bath beckons you with the promise of luxury, comfort, and breathtaking surroundings. As you approach, the open landscaping welcomes you with serenity, setting the stage for the extraordinary residence that awaits.  Step into a world of elegance as you explore the spacious interiors adorned with brand new windows, allowing natural lighting throughout. The recent siding replacement with hardy concrete board not only enhances the property’s value, but also ensures durability for years to come. Indulge in the epitome of relaxation in your very own enclosed pool, a private oasis perfect for unwinding or entertaining guests. Enjoy the warm embrace of the water while relishing the greenbelt views!     This property is not just a home; it’s a haven of efficiency and sustainability. Roof was replaced in 2019, boasting solar electric panels, not only reducing your carbon footprint but also providing long-term savings on energy costs. Additionally, a brand-new septic system has been installed, ensuring seamless functionality, along with many other upgrades (see below).    One of the standout features of this property is its convenient lake access- an invitation to explore water-based activities or simply bask in the tranquility of lakeside living. Whether you’re an outdoor enthusiast or someone seeking a peaceful retreat, 3181 Whisper Wind Dr. effortlessly combines the best of both worlds, priced to sell and won't last long!     In summary, this meticulously maintained property offers:    •4 bedrooms/2.5 bathrooms  •Enclosed Pool  •Greenbelt Views  •Lake Access for water enthusiasts  •Brand new double pane windows  •Siding replaced with hardy concrete boards for durability  •Roof replaced (2019) w/ solar electric panels   •Brand new septic system for seamless functionality (2023)  •Brand new exterior paint (2024)  •Outdoor landscaping   •New indoor light fixtures    Don’t miss the chance to make this house your home- where luxury meets efficiency, and every detail is crafted for a life well-lived. Schedule a showing today and step into a world of comfort, style, and tranquility!
